        <h1>Business welcomes Games transport 'hot spot' information to ensure London is 'open for business' in 2012</h1>
        <div class="content-page-press-release">
        30 November 2011
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="main-and-aside r">
    <div class="main" role="main">

    <div class="article-teaser">
        Transport for London (TfL) of London has released 2012 Games transport 'hot spot' information and advice, which will enable businesses to finalise their plans and ensure the capital is 'open for business' throughout next summer.
        
    </div>



<div class="pull-quote">
